title: Bug 134488 - Setting page break for table inside list group header causes data display error
description: When setting a page break for a table inside a list group header, there is a data display error.
OB: When setting a page break for a table inside a list group header, data is not displaying correctly.
EB: Please see the attached report for details. The expected result is that the data should display correctly. However, in the Web Viewer, the data in the table keeps displaying the first data row in each page, while in HTML/PDF formats, the data displays correctly.
SR: Investigate and fix the issue causing data display errors when setting a page break for a table inside a list group header.
